[SN]TITLE[SN]
Michelin Ballymena: Factory closure will be 'devastating' says union

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
The forthcoming closure of the Michelin tyre factory in Ballymena will be "devastating" for the County Antrim town, according to Unite the Union.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
3 November 2015 Last updated at 13:31 GMT
Unite's regional coordinating officer, Davy Thompson, said it would not only affect the 860 staff, but would have a knock-on effect on hundreds more suppliers and subcontractors.
